License Issue of AMOS After a period of time, the AMOS software may raised the following issue. &ldquo;the temporary period for running amos without a license has expired use the license authorization wizard to contact spss for a license code&rdquo;
Here is the solution to solve this problem.
Go to &ldquo;C:\Program Files (x86)\IBM\SPSS\Amos\26&rdquo;
Delete the file called &ldquo;lservrc&rdquo; (also please save a copy as a backup)
Go to &ldquo;C:\ProgramData\SafeNet Sentinel\Sentinel RMS Development Kit\System&rdquo; and delete all the files inside this folder
